processes.temporal

Class TimeProcess

  • java.lang.Object
    • processes.Process
      • processes.temporal.TimeProcess
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExponentialInverse, Tick

    public abstract class TimeProcess
extends Process
    Convenience superclass for time-specific processes, including some methods for calculating elapsed time. Probably not necessary to have a separate superclass for this.

    At the moment, TimeProcess is specific to a particular cell layer.
